data.description: A beautiful drive leads up to this traditional and spacious two-story, well-maintained home. The formal dining room, family room, and updated kitchen offer a stunning view of the landscaped backyard. Entertain in the finished basement. In addition to the large four bedrooms on the second floor, there is also an additional walk up storage area on the third floor! Situated on 1.96 acres in the Tawa Ridge subdivision offering a rural setting and pond! Liberty Benton school district and only minutes from Findlay.
